extends layout 

block content
  .img-container
    .row.nav
        ul.col-sm-12
          li.inline.col-sm-1  Home
          li.inline.col-sm-1  How? 
          li.inline.col-sm-1  Why? 
          li.inline.col-sm-1  Pricing 
          li.inline.col-sm-2  Send a Note! 
      .row
        .col-sm-12.spacer
      .row
        .col-sm-offset-2.col-sm-4.title
          p  Stand 
          p  Out 
      .row
        .col-sm-offset-2.col-sm-4.subtitle
          p  We send beautiful handwritten notes.
          p  You take the credit. 
    .row.info
      .col-sm-12
        p
          | Others text, tweet, and email. Be remembered with a handwritten note.
          br
          | 				It's the small touches that make a big difference. That really ring home.
          br
          | 				Let us help you make a difference with a handwritten note.
    .row
      .col-sm-12
        h2  How does it work? 
    .explainer
      .row.explainer-margin-1
        .col-sm-offset-4.col-sm-3
          p.write  Write 
          p  Send us your message! 
          p
          p  We'll get scribing. 
          p
        .icon.col-sm-offset-1.col-sm-1
          i.fa.fa-pencil
      .row.explainer-margin
        .icon.col-sm-offset-4.col-sm-1
          i.fa.fa-envelope
        .col-sm-offset-3.col-sm-4
          p.send  We Post It 
          p  We'll send it out on specialty
          p
          p  paper and a high-grade envelope.
          p
      .row.explainer-margin
        .col-sm-offset-4.col-sm-3
          p.send  Respect 
          p  Sleep well knowing the recipient 
          p
          p  knows you care. 
          p
        .icon.col-sm-offset-1.col-sm-1
          i.fa.fa-heart
    .why
      .row.why-title
        .col-sm-12
          h2  Why? 
      .row
        .col-sm-6.img-container-2
        .col-sm-6.info
          p
            | We know what you're thinking. Why bother? Is it really worth it?
            br
            | 				In short, yes. We can guarantee you that these notes will be read and remembered.
            br
            | 				A person goes out of their way to help you, you remember.				
            br
            | 				Why? Because it's so rare these days.
            br
            | 				Be one of the few. Show you care with a Nice Note.
    .pricing-container
      .row
        .col-sm-12
          h2  Pricing 
          h3  I need to send a: 
      .row.button-margin
        .col-sm-12.pricing
          li.note-button.inline  Note 
          li.letter-button.inline  Letter 
      .note-display.center
        //- Icons
        .row
          .col-sm-4.icon-2
            i.fa.fa-eur
          .col-sm-4.icon-2
            i.fa.fa-fighter-jet
          .col-sm-4.icon-2
            i.fa.fa-certificate
            i.fa.fa-certificate
            i.fa.fa-certificate
        //- Row 1
        .row.center
          .col-sm-4
            h3  Flat Price - €3
            br
            p.size
              | Just €3 to send a note! 
              strong  Up to 60 words. 
              | 
          .col-sm-4
            h3  Fast Turnaround
            br
            p.size  All notes will be sent within 1 working day.
            p
          .col-sm-4
            h3  Speciality Paper and Envelope
            br
            p.size
              | We buy high grade envelopes and paper - but not over the top. They suit any occassion.
        //- Row 2
        .row.center
          .col-sm-4.icon-2
            i.fa.fa-lock
          .col-sm-4.icon-2
            i.fa.fa-times
          .col-sm-4.icon-2
            i.fa.fa-camera-retro
        .row
          .col-sm-4
            h3  Confidential 
            br
            p.size
              | All notes are 100% confidential. They are deleted from our database once sent.
          .col-sm-4
            h3.brand-profile-header  No Branding
            br
            p.size
              | Our paper and envelopes have no branding, and are simply quality all the way through.
          .col-sm-4
            h3  Photograph of Note 
            br
            p.size  We'll send you a photograph of the note once it has been sent. 
